      "writtenOn": "2019-12-11T13:18:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "IIUC, this checkout will be located in a directory specified by the config file.  If we\u0027re going to \"git push\" the changes, is there any reason not to perform a fresh checkout in a temporary dir and avoid the possibility of dirty checkouts?",
